    </p>
    <MoneyCTABox store="Baby V" affiliateUrl="https://go.adt231.net/t/t?a=1487384745&as=2065068845&t=2&tk=1&cupa_sku=11001010&url=https://www.babyv.se/sv/articles/1.107.176/stokke-tripp-trapp-matstol" />

    <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-6">2. Cybex Lemo Matstol Suede Grey, bäst design och ergonomi</h2>
