    <MoneyCTABox store="Baby V" affiliateUrl="https://go.adt231.net/t/t?a=1487384745&as=2065068845&t=2&tk=1&cupa_sku=1HC17101HRIGL&url=https://www.babyv.se/sv/articles/1.107.24387/nuna-bryn-matstol-heritage" />

    <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-6">4. Beemoo CARE Eat Matstol, bäst komfort</h2>
